title: Kuhestan, Kerman
content:
Kuhestan (Persian: كوهستان, also Romanized as Kūhestān; also known as Kūhestak)[1] is a village in Kuhestan Rural District, Jazmurian District, Rudbar-e Jonubi County, Kerman Province, Iran. At the 2006 census, its population was 28, in 8 families.[2]
